    <briefdescription>
<para>The class <computeroutput><ref refid="classCGAL_1_1Surface__mesh__simplification_1_1Bounded__normal__change__filter" kindref="compound">Bounded_normal_change_filter</ref></computeroutput> is a model for the <computeroutput><ref refid="classPlacementFilter" kindref="compound">PlacementFilter</ref></computeroutput> concept. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>It rejects a placement if the nested filter rejects it, or if any triangle in the profile changes the normal by more than 90 degree, in this order.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Filter</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>must be a model of the concept <computeroutput><ref refid="classPlacementFilter" kindref="compound">PlacementFilter</ref></computeroutput>. It defaults to a class that does not filter any placement.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<variablelist>
